    join patient p1 on t1.patientunitstayid = p1.patientunitstayid
    join cost c1 on t1.treatmentid = c1.eventid
where 
    p1.age between '50' and '59'
    and datetime(t1.treatmenttime,'start of year') = datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','start of year')
group by 
    t1.treatmentname
order by 
    procedure_count desc
limit 
    4;

input: until 3 years ago, what are the top four commonly ordered drugs f
predict:
select 
    t1.drugname, 
    count(*) as prescription_count
from 
    medication 
    join patient on medication.patientunitstayid = patient.patientunitstayid 
    join diagnosis on patient.uniquepid = diagnosis.uniquepid 
where 
    patient.age between '30' and '39' 
    and datetime(medication.drugstarttime) <= datetime('2105-12-31 23:59:00','-3 year') 
group by 
    t1.drugname 
order by 
    prescription_count desc 
limit 4;

    io.celllabel,
